Empty Character

Send Empty Messages to your Friends

What is this?

This is a funny little utility that will allow you to copy a special character that allows you to send empty messages, email and anything that requires an input. I know that other 1000 apps like this are available online and for this reason i decided to completely remove ads, purchases and (from version 2.0.1 or later) anonymous tracking, so the app is simply free
